## Evidence

The evidence is organized by test scenario to improve readability and traceability.

- **pdf-upload** → Evidence related to PDF upload tests  
- **image-upload** → Evidence related to image upload tests  
- **text-input** → Evidence related to manual text input tests  

Each folder contains step-by-step screenshots demonstrating the reproduction of the identified issues.

